You have to flash TWRP again. Then copy the zip to internal storage (just connect the cable and it will show up as normal) then just install.

The fast dash charge is firmware based, not OS based.
Your phone has a chip inside that talks with the charger and asks for the required voltage and current. Flashing ROM will not impact the performance of charging.

Note :- Oxygen OS is very good in and of itself. You shouldn't flash anything else. That's one of the main reasons people buy OnePlus devices, their great software optimisations and support.
